msg: Added a logging controller class that enables a performant short circuiting of logging tests without sacrificing the ability to enable tracing without requiring recycling of the JVM or flushing classes.  To disable the ability to turn on debug/trace level logging and thereby increase performance, set the system property Axis2.prohibitDebugLogging
